Sentencas: Metallic bi-layer of porous Ni and porous stainless steel (STS) is utilized as a support for micro-solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) using a thin-film layer of electrolyte.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on a porous metallic Ni/stainless-steel bi-layer

Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on a porous metallic Ni/stainless-steel bi-layer

Sentencas: STS-layer covered with a thin (similar to 20 mu m) nano-porous Ni layer.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on a porous metallic Ni/stainless-steel bi-layer

Sentencas: Successful deposition of a nearly pore-free electrolyte layer by the pulsed laser deposition (PLO) method is demonstrated by the high open-circuit-voltage (OCV) value of a single cell.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on a porous metallic Ni/stainless-steel bi-layer

Sentencas: The Ohmic resistance of the micro-SOFC deposited on a porous Ni/STS-support is stable and it shows similar to 28 mW cm(-2) after operation for similar to 112 h at 450 degrees C.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on a porous metallic Ni/stainless-steel bi-layer

Sentencas: The use of a porous Ni/STS bi-layer as a support for micro-SOFCs is successfully demonstrated.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on a porous metallic Ni/stainless-steel bi-layer
